        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Choosing the Right Database Abstraction]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[Dave writes: 'A question came up recently in the Perl community asking whether, in a Mojolicious application, it’s better to use DBIx::Class or a Mojolicious-specific module like Mojo::Pg. It's an interesting question, but I think it's asking the wrong thing.']]></description>
            <pubDate>2026.06.28</pubDate>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://perlhacks.com/2026/06/choosing-the-right-database-abstraction/</guid>
            <link>https://perlhacks.com/2026/06/choosing-the-right-database-abstraction/</link>
            
            
            
